holes.original_proof:
rw [h₁]
simp [Real.zero_rpow (by positivity : ((1 : ℝ) / n : ℝ) ≠ 0)]

apply Finset.prod_le_prod
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]

apply Finset.prod_nonneg
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]

apply Finset.prod_nonneg
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]

exact
  Real.rpow_le_rpow (by positivity) h₉
    (by
      have h₁₃ : (0 : ℝ) ≤ (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
      linarith)

rw [h₂]
simp [Real.zero_rpow (by positivity : ((1 : ℝ) / n : ℝ) ≠ 0)]

apply Finset.prod_le_prod
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]

apply Finset.prod_nonneg
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]

apply Finset.prod_nonneg
intro i _
linarith [abnneg i]

exact
  Real.rpow_le_rpow (by positivity) h₁₀
    (by
      have h₁₄ : (0 : ℝ) ≤ (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
      linarith)

classical
  calc
  ∏ i : Fin n, a i = ∏ i : Fin n, a i := rfl
  _ = 0 := by
    apply Finset.prod_eq_zero (Finset.mem_univ i)
    simp [h₇]

classical
  calc
  ∏ i : Fin n, b i = ∏ i : Fin n, b i := rfl
  _ = 0 := by
    apply Finset.prod_eq_zero (Finset.mem_univ i)
    simp [h₈]

intro i
linarith [h₃ i, h₄ i]

apply Finset.prod_pos
intro i _
exact h₃ i

apply Finset.prod_pos
intro i _
exact h₄ i

apply Finset.prod_pos
intro i _
exact h₅ i

rw [show (∏ i : Fin n, a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) = ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) by
    rw [← Finset.prod_rpow] <;> simp [h₁₀.le, h₆.le, Real.rpow_nonneg, (abnneg _).1] <;> positivity]

rw [show (∏ i : Fin n, b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) = ∏ i : Fin n, ((b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) by
    rw [← Finset.prod_rpow] <;> simp [h₁₁.le, h₇.le, Real.rpow_nonneg, (abnneg _).2] <;> positivity]

rw [show (∏ i : Fin n, (a i + b i : ℝ)) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) = ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) by
    rw [← Finset.prod_rpow] <;>
        simp [h₁₂.le, h₈.le, Real.rpow_nonneg, (by linarith [h₃ 0, h₄ 0] : (0 : ℝ) ≤ a 0 + b 0)] <;>
      positivity]

calc
  (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
    by
    have h₅₁ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
    have h₅₂ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
    have h₅₃ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
    have h₅₄ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
    have h₅₅ : (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
      by
      have h₅₆ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
      have h₅₇ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
      have h₅₈ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
      have h₅₉ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
      calc
        (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
          by
          have h₆₀ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
          have h₆₁ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
          have h₆₂ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
          have h₆₃ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
          have h₆₄ : (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
            by
            have h₆₅ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
            have h₆₆ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
            have h₆₇ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
            have h₆₈ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
            calc
              (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
                by
                have h₆₉ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
                have h₇₀ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
                have h₇₁ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
                have h₇₂ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
                exact?
              _ = (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) := by rfl
          exact h₆₄
        _ = (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) := by rfl
    exact h₅₅
  _ = (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) := by rfl

calc
  (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
    by
    have h₆₀ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
    have h₆₁ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
    have h₆₂ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
    have h₆₃ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
    have h₆₄ : (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
      by
      have h₆₅ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
      have h₆₆ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
      have h₆₇ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
      have h₆₈ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
      calc
        (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
          by
          have h₆₉ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
          have h₇₀ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
          have h₇₁ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
          have h₇₂ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
          exact?
        _ = (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) := by rfl
    exact h₆₄
  _ = (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) := by rfl

calc
  (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
    by
    have h₆₉ : 0 < (a i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₃ i
    have h₇₀ : 0 < (b i : ℝ) := by exact_mod_cast h₄ i
    have h₇₁ : 0 < (a i + b i : ℝ) := by linarith
    have h₇₂ : 0 < (1 : ℝ) / n := by positivity
    exact?
  _ = (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) := by rfl

calc
  (∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) + (∏ i : Fin n, ((b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) ≤
      ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) :=
    by
    have h₂₅ : ∀ i : Fin n, (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
      by
      intro i
      exact h₁₆ i
    calc
      (∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) + (∏ i : Fin n, ((b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) ≤
          ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) :=
        by
        have h₂₆ :
          ∀ i : Fin n, (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
          by
          intro i
          exact h₁₆ i
        calc
          (∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) + (∏ i : Fin n, ((b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) ≤
              ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) :=
            by
            have h₂₇ :
              ∀ i : Fin n, (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
              by
              intro i
              exact h₁₆ i
            calc
              (∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) + (∏ i : Fin n, ((b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) ≤
                  ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) :=
                by
                have h₂₈ :
                  ∀ i : Fin n,
                    (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
                  by
                  intro i
                  exact h₁₆ i
                calc
                  (∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) + (∏ i : Fin n, ((b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) ≤
                      ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) :=
                    by
                    have h₂₉ :
                      ∀ i : Fin n,
                        (a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) ≤ (a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) :=
                      by
                      intro i
                      exact h₁₆ i
                    calc
                      (∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) + (∏ i : Fin n, ((b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n))) =
                          ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n) + (b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) :=
                        by simp [Finset.prod_add]
                      _ ≤ ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) :=
                        by
                        apply Finset.prod_le_prod
                        · intro i _
                          positivity
                        · intro i _
                          exact h₁₆ i
                  _ = ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) := by rfl
              _ = ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) := by rfl
          _ = ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) := by rfl
      _ = ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) := by rfl
  _ = ∏ i : Fin n, ((a i + b i : ℝ) ^ ((1 : ℝ) / n)) := by rfl
